trans-unit.source: Azure API Management REST API Subscription entity
trans-unit.target: Azure API Management REST API Subscription entity

trans-unit.source: The Subscription entity represents the association between a user and a product in <token>azure_apimgt_3</token>.
trans-unit.target: The Subscription entity represents the association between a user and a product in <token>azure_apimgt_3</token>.

trans-unit.source: Products contain one or more APIs, and once a product is published, developers can subscribe to the product and begin to use the product’s APIs.
trans-unit.target: Products contain one or more APIs, and once a product is published, developers can subscribe to the product and begin to use the product’s APIs.

trans-unit.source: This topic describes how to manage subscriptions using the <token>azure_apimgt_3</token> REST API.
trans-unit.target: This topic describes how to manage subscriptions using the <token>azure_apimgt_3</token> REST API.
